          "content_hash": "ee7565c3e859d21f",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "欠intern一堆钱"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "d91e816d5556dc48",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "猛猛pua人，拿推荐信威胁"
        },
        {
          "content_hash": "7fe96578b313050e",
          "style": "NORMAL_TEXT",
          "text": "让intern去自己startup免费打工，需要采购不给报销让intern贴钱"
